EN: The navy has strict requirements for training and equipment.

ZH: 海军在海岸线上设有许多基地。
EN: The navy has many bases along the coast.

ZH: 海军飞机在海上执行侦察任务。
EN: Naval aircraft carry out reconnaissance missions at sea.

ZH: 我的父亲是一名海军军官。
EN: My father is a navy officer.

ZH: 海军需要具备高度机动性。
EN: The navy needs to have high mobility.

ZH: 海军的舰船在夜间会启用雷达。
EN: Naval vessels use radar at night.

ZH: 海军在训练中注重团队合作。
EN: The navy emphasizes teamwork in training.

ZH: 海军士兵需要经常进行体能训练。
EN: Navy sailors need to undergo regular physical training.

