EN: The navy has a strict monitoring system at sea.

ZH: 海军在维护国家安全中扮演着重要角色。
EN: The navy plays a crucial role in safeguarding national security.

ZH: 海军拥有最先进的战舰和装备。
EN: The navy has the most advanced warships and equipment.
